{"tid":1667141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打有玩開水火箭？","createTime":"2019-10-21T09:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T19:07:46.000Z","uid":52817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c39a3e44baa3b604ec956cddb62a1f0e51bb1c50","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"黎緊學校比賽，上網研究左好耐都搵唔到，全部教學都係教點整，但想射得遠同穩定有咩重點？"},{"pid":"f60541ca53972b0d6af5298f5eb9eef978eeb04c","tid":1667141,"uid":20984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39a3e44baa3b604ec956cddb62a1f0e51bb1c50","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"黎緊學校比賽，上網研究左好耐都搵唔到，全部教學都係教點整，但想射得遠同穩定有咩重點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"睇下幾遠，  其實唔洗整個定風翼 用角度加壓力來test 個距離就得。唔好定風翼！"},{"pid":"22f3a93740475299e03997d61db4cbfee4324604","tid":1667141,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"555f3a1ec0fbf64d5024a6e6cdc610e479262b00","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f60541ca53972b0d6af5298f5eb9eef978eeb04c","tid":1667141,"uid":20984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39a3e44baa3b604ec956cddb62a1f0e51bb1c50","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"黎緊學校比賽，上網研究左好耐都搵唔到，全部教學都係教點整，但想射得遠同穩定有咩重點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"睇下幾遠，  其實唔洗整個定風翼 用角度加壓力來test 個距離就得。唔好定風翼！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:56:02.000Z","msg":"定風翼原來冇用既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b44e68cfb7fdbd29d3be0e6a4097eaf7bc9a26","tid":1667141,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632595c5a121467158a714a76d2326580ec90de8","tid":1667141,"uid":125380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"每個學生必玩既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1504913a35bb616b0ee49346ca14ecf078993405","tid":1667141,"uid":20262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"想玩返，但香港好難搵到空地做試驗"},{"pid":"2e3e62a6af8813fb72a473667274c452743b1b99","tid":1667141,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"可樂好玩啲<br />\n加少少野<br />\nchok兩野就射出去<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/vVwnrD.gif?fit=480%2C270&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fboingboing.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2FvVwnrD.gif%3Ffit%3D480%252C270%26ssl%3D1&h=8e90558e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20790fa027b8ea1737ab7f98642d571649cdce36","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e3e62a6af8813fb72a473667274c452743b1b99","tid":1667141,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"可樂好玩啲<br />\n加少少野<br />\nchok兩野就射出去<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/vVwnrD.gif?fit=480%2C270&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fboingboing.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2FvVwnrD.gif%3Ffit%3D480%252C270%26ssl%3D1&h=8e90558e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:12:59.000Z","msg":"會亂飛"},{"pid":"53589a7e9c773094442ceceb4facacac54636af2","tid":1667141,"uid":271353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"其實一支充氣泵加幾支水樽就搞掂 威力都唔差 幾年前唔小心比人誤射中眼 差啲以為自己會盲"},{"pid":"3e5d7a39a6f5ff80a4cedd5c0d2f1adf103b8869","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53589a7e9c773094442ceceb4facacac54636af2","tid":1667141,"uid":271353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:13:39.000Z","msg":"其實一支充氣泵加幾支水樽就搞掂 威力都唔差 幾年前唔小心比人誤射中眼 差啲以為自己會盲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"好易TK喎尤其是係上面裝左野 起碼要有個發射架"},{"pid":"0eb2b9e91964c39733ea54a183393358dcb0e219","tid":1667141,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"e6d856956129a5bc592066ea25a3c1a20a9b9d85","tid":1667141,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"對翼應該要硬同大啲"},{"pid":"1c3ae1212d766b3039c599b1aa6a11ebfa60a8b7","tid":1667141,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:24:06.000Z","msg":"我估個口都可能有少少功夫，可能要螺旋噴，增加正向性"},{"pid":"66090735f6b2befc80629d1fae6bdef8f8978834","tid":1667141,"uid":20984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6d856956129a5bc592066ea25a3c1a20a9b9d85","tid":1667141,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:22:55.000Z","msg":"對翼應該要硬同大啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:05:33.000Z","msg":"裝左反而會飄，如果唔係90度飛，如果最遠一定係45度唔加翼，同埋睇幾多枝樽"},{"pid":"7cd1262207041bcf8fdef9d0fbe7bd20cc54d77f","tid":1667141,"uid":20984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555f3a1ec0fbf64d5024a6e6cdc610e479262b00","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f60541ca53972b0d6af5298f5eb9eef978eeb04c","tid":1667141,"uid":20984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39a3e44baa3b604ec956cddb62a1f0e51bb1c50","tid":1667141,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"黎緊學校比賽，上網研究左好耐都搵唔到，全部教學都係教點整，但想射得遠同穩定有咩重點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:10.000Z","msg":"睇下幾遠，  其實唔洗整個定風翼 用角度加壓力來test 個距離就得。唔好定風翼！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:56:02.000Z","msg":"定風翼原來冇用既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T19:07:46.000Z","msg":"係，以前聯校比賽個個都係整定風翼，得我地無整比人笑，跟住反而係最遠最穩定，一個藍球場距離。我地係比賽遠同射target ，如果射目標就要自己整多幾個角度去試個距離，要瘋狂test + mark返啲數據。"}]}